    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to someone but what's the point? doctors just give me pills that make me groggy and the pain still stays. it's not like it's going to get better. it just feels like a slow, agonizing way to exist. sometimes i just think how much easier it would be if everything just... stopped. if there was just peace and no more sensation.",
